# Leetcode套路总结

推荐题库

 - Blind 75

## Linked list

 - Basic traversal. Consistent node relationship.
 - Cover all edge cases
   - Empty list
   - Single node where the head is also the tail
   - When removing or adding nodes, will new tail/head be created?
   - Head and tail handling
 - If multiple methods modify nodes, are they consistent? They need to
   follow the same requirements.
 - If there are multiple lists to be handled, check boundaries of all
   lists. Make sure no list go out of boundary.
 
### 代表题：

 - LRU cache
 - 21. Merge Two Sorted Lists 热身
 - 143. Reorder List 本质不难但是容易翻车

